organization%20is%20accountable%20for%20compliance%20with%20the%20tax%20strategy,%20the%20organization%20can%20specify%20the%20degree%20to%20which%20the&nbsp;highest%20governance%20body%20has%20oversight%20of%20compliance.%20The%20organization%20can%20also%20specify%20any%20accountability%20for%20compliance%20delegated%20to%20executive-level%20positions%20within%20the%20organization.%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E&nbsp;%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Cstrong%3EGuidance%20for%20Disclosure%20207-2-a-ii%20%3C/strong%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20reporting%20how%20the%20approach%20to%20tax%20is%20embedded%20within%20the%20organization,%20the%20organization%20can%20describe%20processes,%20projects,%20programs,%20and%20initiatives%20that%20support%20adherence%20to%20the%20approach%20to%20tax%20and%20tax%20strategy.%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3EExamples%20of%20such%20initiatives%20can%20include:%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E&bull;%20Training%20and%20guidance%20provided%20to%20relevant%20employees%20on%20the%20link%20between%20tax%20strategy,%20business%20strategy,%20and%20sustainable%20development;%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E&bull;%20Remuneration%20or%20incentive%20schemes%20for%20the%20person(s)%20responsible%20for%20implementing%20the%20tax%20strategy;%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E&bull;%20Succession-planning%20for%20positions%20within%20the%20organization%20that%20are%20responsible%20for%20tax;%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E&bull;%20Participation%20in%20tax%20transparency%20initiatives%20or%20representative%20associations%20that%20seek%20to%20develop%20best%20practice%20around%20disclosures%20on%20tax%20or%20educate%20stakeholders%20on%20tax-related%20issues.%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E&nbsp;%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Cstrong%3EGuidance%20for%20Disclosure%20207-2-a-iii%20%3C/strong%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3ETax%20risks%20are%20risks%20associated%20with%20the%20organization&rsquo;s%20tax%20practices%20that%20might%20lead%20to%20a%20negative%20effect%20on%20the%20goals%20of%20the%20organization,%20or%20to%20financial%20or%20reputational